name: Promac Global
overview:
Promac was established with a vision of connecting Companies and Consultants globally to facilitate communication and collaboration towards successful execution of projects and services.

This strategically engineered global business consulting network idea has evolved over a period of time to become an organization with a vision and strategic direction backed by experienced people, tools and technologies across multiple platforms to provide expert consulting services to clients across broad spectrum of industries.

Promac offers consulting services to clients by identifying the right company/consultant/service provider for a project deal, collaboration, merger, acquisition or franchisee by taking in to consideration various factors that measure the quality of work and success.
